description: One day, Larry's lazy day of sitting and smoking is interrupted by two men who complain that they are ugly: one feels that his face is too tall, the other feels his is too flat. The two men, thinking they are twins, hug each other and walk off, thanking Larry and Jagi. Larry reclines back on the sofa.
